ASEC-ATUS Match Quality Statistics

Year 2012

This page contains data evaluating the Match quality of data between ATUS (weekday and weekend) and ASEC.

This is done by comparing the mean, median and Standard deviation for time spent on household production for various selected groups and their interactions
